subgraph Page_33 [Page 33]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_be9f5d5f["13 Service Provision"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_1_dedbf400["13.1 Safety Case Report"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_1_1_98d5f466["13.1.1 The contractor shall produce a<br/>safety case report and command summary<br/>and deliver them to the UK MOD for<br/>approval before commencement of<br/>services."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_1_2_1d227dee["13.1.2 The contractor shall maintain the<br/>safety case, safety case report and<br/>command summary so they are accurate<br/>representations of the service."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_1_3_5158775a["13.1.3 The contractor shall produce<br/>command summaries so that each provision<br/>of the service can be properly assessed<br/>and controlled in terms of risk."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_1_4_4d392af2["13.1.4 The contractor shall provide<br/>information to support domain specific<br/>processes providing essential<br/>information for the accountable person<br/>responsible for the service to manage<br/>risk to life."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_2_0948fbf0["13.2 Service Provision Planning"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_2_1_d68e3c32["13.2.1 The contractor shall produce<br/>plans for management of service<br/>operations, covering all reasonably<br/>foreseeable situations including<br/>abnormal and emergency situations."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_2_2_459299fd["13.2.2 The contractor shall ensure that<br/>the plans cover the safety of the full<br/>range of normal services and operations,<br/>including but not limited to defining<br/>standard operating procedures,<br/>resourcing, training, and oversight<br/>arrangements."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_2_3_a0f4738a["13.2.3 The contractor shall ensure that<br/>the plans cover the safety of emergency<br/>situations, including but not limited to<br/>defining emergency response,<br/>coordination and decision making,<br/>including liaison with the service<br/>accountable person and relevant<br/>stakeholders."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_2_4_d5674ada["13.2.4 The contractor shall ensure that<br/>these plans cover safe update, including<br/>ways of making changes on continuously<br/>running systems, if necessary, building<br/>on installation instructions supplied<br/>from support, as appropriate."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_2_5_7896e147["13.2.5 The contractor shall ensure that<br/>the communications plan, detailed in the<br/>SMP, includes processes for delivery of<br/>in-service data and build state<br/>definition."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_2_6_971aa302["13.2.6 The contractor shall provide<br/>information to those not employed as<br/>part of the provision of the service<br/>about relevant undertakings, where this<br/>might affect their health and safety.<br/>How this will be achieved shall be<br/>included in the relevant plans."]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_2_7_a0556ac6["13.2.7 The contractor shall provide<br/>access to health and safety advice<br/>relating to the service, and<br/>consultation on the risks to employees,<br/>contractors and any other people who<br/>could be affected by them."]
